longBusinessSummary: K.P. Energy Limited provides balance of plant solutions for wind industry in India. It offers solutions for wind project and wind-solar hybrid project development, which comprises site identification and acquisition, site preparation and logistics, erection, power evacuation, and operations and maintenance services, as well as engineering, procurement, construction, and commissioning services. The company owns and operates four wind energy turbines with a capacity of 14.7 MW and two solar power plants with a capacity of 11.5 MW. K.P. Energy Limited was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Surat, India.
